Package: fastInteraction
Type: Package
Title: Continuous variable interaction output and graphs (2D/3D)
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("David", "Stanley", , "dstanley@uoguelph.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Conducting a moderated regression with continous variables can require a large number of steps which are simplified with this package. Easily create regression objects, 2D/3D surface plots, APA tables for overall/simple slopes, and console output.
